ProcessEntity.path: Transfer.Input.What amount would you like to transfer ?

Attr.original: What amount would you like to transfer ?

ProcessEntity.Note:
Amount field:

 

Inputtable amount field designed with regex. The regex is applied so that the user will be restricted to send invalid characters to the server.

 

Regex Design:

Allowed length: 1 to 19.

Allowed characters: 0123456789.,

 

The same Regex should be applied across all the business components for the inputtable amount fields.

 

The default data store amount item should be plain text and should not be converted to any special type.

Transaction Authentication component is implemented within this business component.
